ing Display","description":"Shows the actual ping number instead of just bars in the player list.","url":"","version":"1.0","authorList":["Quintinity"],"credits":"","requiredMods":[],"dependencies":[],"dependants":[]},{"modid":"biggerchathistory","name":"BiggerChatHistory","description":"","url":"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/biggerchathistory","version":"0.1.1","authorList":["Keksuccino"],"credits":"","requiredMods":[],"dependencies":[],"dependants":[]},{"modid":"biggerpacketsplz","name":"Bigger Packets, please !","description":"Enable reception of compressed packets bigger than 2097152 bytes.\n\nStatus :\nPatches applied\n\nClasses :\n - gy, alias \u0027net.minecraft.network.PacketBuffer\u0027\n","url":"http://mods.mc.elnounch.net/biggerpacketsplz","version":"1.2","authorList":["ElNounch"],"credits":"","requiredMods":[],"dependencies":[],"dependants":[]},{"modid":"bnbgaminglib","name":"BNBGamingLib","description":"Shared library between all BNBGaming mods.","url":"http://bloodnbonesgaming.com/","version":"2.17.6","authorList":["Blargerist, superckl"],"credits":"","requiredMods":[],"dependencies":[{"label":"bnbgamingcore","version":"unknown","range":"any"}],"dependants":[]},{"modid":"bookshelf","name":"Bookshelf","description":"Bookshelf is a core/library mod, which adds new features and tools into the game for other content creators to work with. The primary focus of this project is to make use of the combined strength of the modded community to create wonderful tools that everyone can use.","url":"http://minecraft.curseforge.com/projects/bookshelf","version":"2.3.590","authorList":["darkhax","lclc98"],"credits":"ChickenBones, CyanideX, iLexiconn, SanAndreasP, VikeStep, jaredlll08","requiredMods":[],"dependencies":[],"dependants":[]},{"modid":"brandonscore","name":"Brandon\u0027s Core","description":"Brandon\u0027s Core is a library mod used by most of my mods. It is no longer a core mod as the name would suggest but it does still contain a lot of the core code used by my mods including but not limited to base classes for various tiles, blocks and items, A powerful modular gui system and a lot of other miscellaneous utilities.","url":"http://minecraft.curseforge.com/projects/brandons-core","version":"1.12.2-2.4.20.22","authorList":["brandon3055"],"credits":"","requiredMods":[{"label":"redstoneflux","version":"unknown","range":"any"},{"label":"codechickenlib","version":"unknown","range":"[3.2.0,)"}],"dependencies":[{"label":"codechickenlib","version":"unknown","range":"[3.2.0,)"},{"label":"redstoneflux","version":"unknown","range":"any"}],"dependants":[]},{"modid":"ceramics","name":"Ceramics","description":"Adds a few early game items based on baking clay","url":"https://minecraft.curseforge.com/projects/ceramics","version":"1.12-1.3.7b","authorList":["KnightMiner"],"credits":"Much of the code for clay buckets is based off the Forge universal bucket","requiredMods":[{"label":"forge","version":"unknown","range":"[14.21.1.2394,)"}],"dependencies":[{"label":"forge","version":"unknown","range":"[14.21.1.2394,)"},{"label":"tconstruct","version":"unknown","range":"any"}],"dependants":[]},{"modid":"chambers","name":"Chambers","description":"Chambers are machines that perform the crafting/processing recipes that normally rely on either in-world crafting or multi-block builds.","url":"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/chambers","version":"1.5.2","authorList":["userTravis"],"credits":"","requiredMods":[],"dependencies":[],"dependants":[]},{"modid":"classicbar","name":"Classic Bar","description":"Customizable status bars","url":"https://github.com/Tfarcenim/ClassicBar/","version":"0.5.4","authorList":["Tfarecnim"],"credits":"","requiredMods":[],"dependencies":[{"label":"randomtweaks","version":"unknown","range":"[1.12.2-2.7.1.0,)"}],"dependants":[]},{"modid":"clienttweaks","name":"Client Tweaks","description":"There, I fixed Minecraft for you.","url":"http://balyware.com","version":"3.1.11","authorList":["BlayT